Which of the following glucoses and glucose derivatives are capable of undergoing mutarotation? 

**(a)** $\alpha$-D-Glucopyranose; 

**(b)** methyl $\alpha$-D-glucopyranoside; 

**(c)** methyl $\alpha$-2,3,4,6-tetra-*O*-methyl-d- glucopyranoside (i.e., the tetramethyl ether at carbon 2, 3, 4, and 6); 

**(d)** $\alpha$-2,3,4,6-tetra-*O*-methyl- D-glucopyranose; 

**(e)** $\alpha$-D-glucopyranose 1,2-acetone acetal.
